snippet.title: Dune by Voodoo | Hyper Casual Games | Android iOS game
snippet.description:
#hypercasualgames #androidgames #iosgames
This is my second fan made video game trailer. The game is Dune by Voodoo. Its an amazing endless game with various characters and worlds to unlock. I like the style of Voodoo games as they focus purely on gameplay eliminafing the various navigation screens. Great work. 

My Indie game Love Jump :
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gamethics.love.jump
